text: Chésopelloz (Dictionnaire-Dikchenéro: Français-Patois/Patê-Franché. Société cantonale des patoisans fribourgeois. Fribourg: 2013. ) was a municipality of the district Saane in the canton of Fribourg in Switzerland. The former municipality of Chésopelloz on 1 January 2017, merged into Corminboeuf.Amtliches Gemeindeverzeichnis der Schweiz accessed 10 January 2017 == References == ==Other websites== Category:Former municipalities of Fribourg
